(define/contract (make-the-integer-zero num1 num2)
  (-> exact-integer? exact-integer? exact-integer?)
  (letrec ((min-ops (lambda (num ops)
                      (if (= num 0)
                          ops
                          (let loop ((i 0) (best #f))
                            (if (> i 60)
                                best
                                (let* ((subtraction (+ (expt 2 i) num2))
                                       (next-num (- num subtraction)))
                                  (if (and (>= next-num 0) (or (not best) (< i best)))
                                      (loop (+ i 1) (if (zero? next-num) i best))
                                      best)))))))
            (result (min-ops num1 0)))
    (if result result -1)))
